name: Peter Gersten
description: I’m Peter Gersten by name. United States Airforce General, am presently in Northern Syria in charge of the airstrikes against the Islamic State rebels, and am the Deputy Commander-Operations and Intelligence (O&I), Combined Joint Task Force-Operation Inherent Resolve, U.S. Central Command; and Commander, 9th Air Expeditionary Task Force-Levant (9AETF-L), Air Combat Command, Southwest Asia. I’m 53.
